data.description: Embrace your dream home in South Carson City, a 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, 3-car garage, 3182 sq ft sanctuary on 1 acre. Revel in panoramic Pine Nut Mountain views, wind-sheltered rolling hills, and potential for horses. Delight in expansive great room living, 2 master bedrooms in a single-story haven. Impeccably kept, flooded with natural light, boasting 10 ft ceilings, and a thoughtfully open layout, this home offers an inviting ambiance in every corner. No HOA and just minutes from major amenities. 360 tour available on Virtual Tour - Modern luxury defines this open-floor plan home with Maple wood cabinetry, energy-efficient appliances, Nest thermostats, Tesla charger, and Ring doorbell. Enjoy stunning views beyond the property's ridge, perfect for a gazebo. Relax in the spa-like primary bath with Toto bidet, custom walk-in closet, and vanity mirror extension. With an oversized garage, Hydrant Talco fire system, Bio Microbics septic, and Philips HueLights, this home is the epitome of comfort and style  ROOM MEASUREMENTS  Primary: 26' x 17' | 388 sq ft  ***  Primary Bath: 16'6" x 14'8" | 213 sq ft  ***  Primary Closet: 8'6" x 14'8" | 118 sq ft  ***  Junior Suite: 13'8" x 12'4" | 145 sq ft  ***  Junior Suite Bath: 9'1" x 5'9" | 50 sq ft  ***  Bedroom 3: 11'6" x 21'5" | 198 sq ft  ***  Bedroom 4: 12'4" x 12'8" | 157 sq ft  ** Bedroom 3 and Bedroom 4 with Jack and Jill bath  ***  Half Bath: 5'6" x 5'1" | 28 sq ft  ***  Great: 18'5" x 19'2" | 353 sq ft  ***  Formal Dining: 17'1" x 12'2" | 208 sq ft  ***  Kitchen: 21'2" x 19'2" | 392 sq ft  ***  Pantry: 7'3" x 6'7"  ***  Laundry: 7'8" x 8' | 62 sq ft  ***  3+ Car Garage: 31' x 33'10" | 904 sq ft
